attachmentList.title: Higher_Longevity.png
attachmentList.detail:
Higher Longevity:
The cartridges are tested 5 lakh times to ensure a longer and trouble free operating life.

attachmentList.title: Advanced_Water.png
attachmentList.detail:
Advanced water saving flow restrictor:
It restricts the water flow up to 1.3* ltr per min at 3 bar pressure.

attachmentList.title: Operates_Smoothly.png
attachmentList.detail:
Operates smoothly:
Wide-angle lever provides increased comfort and flawless smooth operation.

attachmentList.title: Optimum_Flow.png
attachmentList.detail:
Optimum flow and temperature:
The faucets work smoothly at high temperature (up to 85 degree) and various pressure conditions (0.5 to 5 bar).

attachmentList.title: Unmatched_warranty.png
attachmentList.detail:
Unmatched warranty:
Up to 10 years warranty.

attachmentList.title: Soft_Water_Flow.png
attachmentList.detail:
Soft water flow:
Aerators Integrated with honeycomb structure give protection from lime buildup and provide soft flow of water.

attachmentList.title: Higher_Durability.png
attachmentList.detail:
Higher Durability:
High plating thickness (Nickel 10 micron & chrome 0.3 micron) provides tolerance to extreme climate and water conditions.

attachmentList.title: click_position_system_icon.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Click Position System
All Jaquar multi-function showers feature the convenient click mechanism. You can feel and hear the click while changing the function of the shower sprays.

attachmentList.title: jaquar_booster_technology_icon.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Jaquar Booster Technology
Jaquar Booster Technology creates the sensation of a full shower regardless of the water pressure.

attachmentList.title: thermo_insulation_icon.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Thermo Insulation
Jaquar insulated shower systems prevent scalding by not heating up the shower body.

attachmentList.title: advanced_rubitt_technology_icon.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Advanced Rubit Technology
This technology keeps showers clean and increases their longevity. The spray jets on the showers are made from elastic silicon, which ensure that no lime scale deposits stick to the shower face.

attachmentList.title: Multi_function.png
attachmentList.detail:
Multi-function Safety Valve
discharges water and acts as a non-return valve if pressure or temperature exceed preset limit.

attachmentList.title: earthlekage-circuit-breaker.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Earth Leakage Circuit Breaker
The ELCB is designed to prevent shock and injury to users. It quickly disconnects a circuit whenever detecting an imbalance of electric current leakage through the body of a person who is grounded and accidentally touching the electriferous part of the circuit.

attachmentList.title: High_Density_Insulation.png
attachmentList.detail:
High Density Insulation
CFC-free PUF-insulation, extra thick than normal to minimise heatloss and maximise energy savings.

attachmentList.title: 7year-warranty-water-heater.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
7 Years Warranty*
On Tank

attachmentList.title: Cathodic_Protection.png
attachmentList.detail:
Cathodic Protection
a sacrificial Magnesium Anode protects and saves the tank from electrochemical reactions during water heating.

attachmentList.title: Superior_Quality.png
attachmentList.detail:
Superior Quality Glass-lined Inner Tank
prevents rust, corrosion and prolongs the life of the inner tank.

attachmentList.title: Double_Safety.png
attachmentList.detail:
Double Safety Thermostat
dual overheating control mechanism cuts off power automatically even if primary cut off fails.

attachmentList.title: element-waterheater.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Faster Heating
Single/Dual Glass-coated Incoloy Heating Elements – made of high quality steel for quicker heating and to prevent scale formation

attachmentList.title: remote-water-heater.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Cathodic Protection
•Cordless Remote 
• Full Digital Display 
• On/Off Timer
• Clock Temperature Setting

products.detail: Ideal for large families and multiple bathrooms with bathtubs and whirlpools

attachmentList.title: after-sales-service.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
After Sales Service
Large service network for complete peace of mind. Jaquar also offers preventive maintenance services for hassle free bathrooms.

attachmentList.title: rimless-features.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Rimless WC
Innovative, hygienic design that makes flushing efficient and cleaning effortless.

attachmentList.title: easy-installation.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Easy Installation:
•Flatness of parts getting fixed to the wall 
•No gaps between the wall, floor and the fitting portions of the sanitaryware 
•Perfect fitting for a perfect look 
•Enlongated rag bolts roles are elliptical in shape, hence it is easy to install

attachmentList.title: anti-germ-glazing.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Anti-Germ Glazing
Anti-Bacterial Glaze is a powerful Fluoro-Polymer coating of 20 to 100 nanometer thickness. It is appliedon Jaquar WCs and Wash Basins through a special process and provides the following benefits: 
• It forms a strong hydrophobic shield which prevents the build-up of bacteria and germs
• Ideal for India’s humid weather conditions 
• Renders the surface durable and highly repellent to dirt, oils and liquids 
• Facilitates easy removal of hard water deposits

attachmentList.title: soft-closing.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Soft Closing Detachable UF Seat Cover
• Load bearing capacity of over 150 kg (seat cover and bushes) 
•Shape and texture of the seats unaffected by temperature variations 
• Does not absorb room temperature therefore the seats are neither too hot nor too cold to touch 
• Surface is resistant to stains and strong dyes 
• Does not deform or peel-off with use 
• Special buffer oil is used in the hinges for lasting functionality 
• Soft-close action to eliminate noise of falling of the cover. This is guaranteed for 2 years 
• Adjustable speed of falling of the cover within a range of 1 to 15 seconds that leads to silent operations

attachmentList.title: uniform-stndard.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Uniform Standard
Uniform grades of product available for retail and project. No differentiation in terms of product quality, design and colour.

attachmentList.title: clean-odourfree-wc.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Clean and Odour-free WCs:
The interior portion of the traps of water closets are glazed 
• Ensures the trap does not collect dirt or give out odour 
• Prevents dirt from sticking inside the trap 
• Facilitates easy flushing and waste removal 
• Ensures clean and odour-free bathroom

attachmentList.detail: 10 Years Warranty

attachmentList.title: The PMMA Advantage.png
attachmentList.detail:
The PMMA Advantage
Jaquar bathtubs are made of the highest grade of PMMA acrylic. Due to the reinforcement with 20mm of plywood at the bottom, the tub doesn’t develop cracks at the bottom when filled with hot water.

attachmentList.title: No Bacteria Formation. Fresh Water Everytime.png
attachmentList.detail:
No Bacteria Formation
The water pipes connect via V-shaped housings, creating a bow which ensures the complete drainage of water. Unpleasant odours and bacteria are thus avoided and you get fresh water every time.

attachmentList.title: 3 Tier Test.png
attachmentList.detail:
3 Tier Test
Each and every Jaquar Whirlpool goes through a functional test with hot water after which it is tested on a European test machine for earthing resistance, insulation test and a high voltage test.

attachmentList.title: water-jets.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Water Jets
The effectiveness of the hydromassage is enhanced by the exclusive performance of the Glass patented “JET CLEAN” nozzles. They have orientable nozzles with partial closing system. The water flow can be adjusted in intensity and direction to suit personal needs, in order to gently massage delicate areas with capillary fragility and give a more energetic massage to areas that need more vascular stimulation

attachmentList.title: Easy To Use.png
attachmentList.detail:
Easy To Use
The digital/manual control activates all the hydromassage functions to regulate Airpool intensity. All electronic parts can be installed and removed on site.

attachmentList.title: airpool-jet.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Airpool Jet
The airpool jets are made of plastic and provide a gentle and delicate massage on your spine, which increases the sensation of warmth in the body and has benefical effects on the back.
When immersed in water, the body builds up a protective layer which insulates the body. The air bubbles open the insulation layer releasing oxygen, and stimulating blood circulation. It optimises the transfer of warmth and the feeling of wellbeing.

attachmentList.title: Environment Friendly.png
attachmentList.detail:
Environment Friendly
The pipes are made from special Food Grade PVC. These pipes have an anti bacterial coating on the inner side so that even if some drops of water stay behind after the tub is drained, there won't be any bacteria formation in the water droplets.

attachmentList.title: Safety Vacuum Breaker.png
attachmentList.detail:
Safety Vacuum Breaker
This is one of the most important safety features installed in Jaquar whirlpools. In case of blockage in the suction point, the motor switches off automatically.

attachmentList.title: Air Suction Valve.png
attachmentList.detail:
Air Suction Valve
There is an additional pipeline in the water circuit which is connected to all the water jets. This pipeline is also connected to a pump with a heating coil which sucks atmospheric air, heats it and distributes it to each and every water jet to boost the jet pressure.

attachmentList.title: cabinet-insulation.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Cabinet Insulation
Jaquar Spas have insulation in the perimeter of their cabinets to maintain the warmth of the water, and the spa's plumbing and equipment, further reducing your energy costs. The insulation system has two features that make it superior to the traditional 'foam on shell' spa insulation system. By insulating the cabinet instead of the shell, Jaquar Spas not only retain heat from the pumps and equipment, but also insulate the plumbing that otherwise would lose heat to the environment. This results in less overall heat loss and lower running costs. What's more, the insulation reduces the noise of the spa pumps so you will also enjoy a quieter, more tranquil spa experience.

attachmentList.title: neck-therepy.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Neck therapy collar
Optional on most Jaquar models, the neck therapy collar incorporates jets specially designed to eliminate stress and tension carried in the neck and shoulder area. Opt for the neck therapy collar to soothe away the stresses of your day.

attachmentList.title: individual-pressure.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Individual pressure control
To ensure complete satisfaction for all, each seat in your Jaquar Spa can be controlled with the seat's pressure control dial. In addition, most jets can be individually controlled, directing pressure to where you need it most.

attachmentList.title: dynamic-lighting.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Dynamic lighting options
Flood lighting, jet lights, backlit drink holders and water features, waterline illumination and access lighting can all be added to your Jaquar Spa to enhance your experience. Lighting programs can be controlled using the spa's topside controller

attachmentList.title: intelligent-thermal.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Intelligent Thermal Regulation
Allows the spa to tune itself to its environment, day-to-day and season-to-season, thus reducing your heating costs by up to 20%. Thermal performance and heat retention is what distinguishes one spa from another. Jaquar's control system adapts and tunes itself to the thermal properties of your spa pool, in its environment, day to day and season to season, to reduce 'on demand' heating. The control system of a Jaquar Spa actually 'learns' how your spa is used. By reducing the temperature drop required before the heater switches on, it provides more consistent spa water temperatures and lowers daily operating costs.

attachmentList.title: ergonomic-design.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Ergonomic design
Jaquar Spa control systems are intuitive and easy to operate and offer maximum flexibility and control. The top side panel controls most functions with one touch of a button. More advanced controls can be accessed through the simple English menu functions.

attachmentList.title: hydroflow-jets.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Hydroflow jets
A Jaquar Spa's hydroflow jets are designed to maximise jet pressure and provide a world-class hydrotherapy experience. We choose from a multitude of directional, spinning and fixed jets to create a different massage action in each seat. Some seats give a broad massage using wide sweep rotational jets, whilst others provide a pinpoint, Shiatsu-style massage.

attachmentList.title: easy-to-operate.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Easy to operate
Jaquar Spa control systems are intuitive and easy to operate and offer maximum flexibility and control. The top side panel controls most functions with one touch of a button. More advanced controls can be accessed through the simple English menu functions.

attachmentList.title: two-seats.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Two lounger seats
To avoid arguments over who gets the spa's lounger (usually the most comfortable and most coveted seat in the spa), most Jaquar Spas have two luxurious hydrotherapy loungers.

attachmentList.title: smart-meter-ready.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Smart meter ready
Even if your electricity provider does not currently offer smart meters, they soon will. A smart meter allows your electricity supplier to charge higher prices in periods of high demand, but rewards consumers who shift their consumption to low demand periods such as overnight. Using Power Save software, Jaquar Spas can be designed to do the filtering and heating when power costs are at their lowest. Best of all, the control is in your hands. You can tailor the operation of your Jaquar Spa to take advantage of smart meter technology and reduce your running costs.

attachmentList.title: purezone-micro.jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Purezone Micro Filtration
The top priority of an effective water treatment system is to remove waterborne contaminants. Conventional filters only trap particles up to 50 microns in size. A luxurious spa experience Jaquar Spas have superior hydrotherapy performance and features that are seen in the world's most expensive spas.

attachmentList.title: icon_shower_enclosure (12).jpg
attachmentList.detail:
Quality checks :
Fragmentation test : to check breakage pattern of glass
• Zebra test: no waviness
• Ball drop test (impact resistance): to check strength at point of impact
• Visual defects: to check bubbles, scratches, chipping at edges and other visible defects
• Free fall test: to check overall strength of glass, by throwing the glass freely on a plain surface
Standards :
• These standards ensure that the glass passes stringent quality parameters
• Ensures consistency
• Enhances life of the product
Conforms to both European and Indian standards
Reference : India
• IS 2553 ( part 1 : 1990 )
• IS 14900 : 2000
• IS 2835 : 1987
Reference : Europe
• En 14450 : 2000
• Adheres to European toughening norms

Perfect Pan Cleaning
Heavy and even water discharge during every flush at every water pressure.

attachmentList.title: icon_less_noise.jpg

Less Noise
Technically advanced, silent flush valve and fast-filling hydraulic float valve minimises the flushing sound during usage.

Anti-condensation lining wraps the tank and supply bend, to protect damage from masonry condensation.

Easy to install and maintain
Jaquar’s floor standing frames with concealed cisterns not only provide the benefits of easy, quick and perfect installation but also allow you to choose modern wall mounted sanitaryware of your choice.
